Educational disclaimer:

This project, *DEX-Edu Support App*, is an **independent educational prototype**
inspired by the ESA concept **DEX — Dark-Ages EXplorer**.  
It is **not affiliated, sponsored, or approved** by the European Space Agency
(ESA) or any of its partners.  
